, weird. Why the lies in this field, it&#39;s so far beyond my comprehension. I=
 run into this disinformation, twist everything around stuff almost daily. =


 Even with the LM3820, you can&#39;t follow the data sheet at all, it&#39;s all =
jacked up! I found an app guide for another FM chip, and they used the LM38=
20 for the AM section, that&#39;s what I went by to use that chip. The LM3820 i=
s 12 cents each, so cost was the motivating factor there. It&#39;s only disadva=
ntage is having to use an external detector stage. 

 The LA1135 is used i=
n the car tuner modules I like to use, so I know it&#39;s capable iof decent pe=
rformance. The datasheet show this as being voltage tuned, so it should be =
exactly what we need. 

